# Package manager scope

| Directory | Manager | Lockfile |
|-----------|---------|----------|
| `Monorepo_ModMe/` (root) | Yarn 3.3 (orchestration only) | `yarn.lock` |
| `GenerativeUI_monorepo/` | Yarn 3.3 | `GenerativeUI_monorepo/yarn.lock` |
| `next-forge/` | Bun | `next-forge/bun.lock` |
| `UniversalWorkbench*/` | Yarn 4.10 | per-copy `yarn.lock` |
| `.cursor/skills/*/scripts/` | pnpm (isolated skill runtimes) | gitignored |

## IDE

- Workspace setting: `"npm.packageManager": "yarn@3.3.0"` at repo root.
- Exclude vendor, tools, and nested monorepo node_modules via `npm.exclude`.

## Commands

```powershell
yarn dev:generative   # GenerativeUI_monorepo
yarn dev:forge        # next-forge (uses npx bun)
```

Never run `yarn install` inside `next-forge/` or `bun install` inside `GenerativeUI_monorepo/`.
